OL,7,FViewers may find some of the details
OL,8,Fof Sara O'Kane's report distressing.
OL,10,FThe surviving daughter of a woman who
OL,11,Fwas killed alongside three other
OL,12,Ffamily members in a house fire in Co
OL,13,FFermanagh has said her life would
OL,14,Fnever be the same again.
OL,16,FA statement from Samantha Gosset was
OL,17,Fread outside Belfast Crown court on
OL,18,FWednesday, .
