OL,7,FThe 33-year-old previously pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to the manslaughter of his
OL,9,Fpartner Denise Gossett and the murder
OL,10,Fof her daughter Sabrina Gossett, 19,
OL,11,Fson Roman Gossett, 16, and Sabrina
OL,12,FGossett's 15-month-old daughter
OL,13,FMorgana Quinn in the deliberate fire
OL,14,Fat a house in Derrylin on 27 February
OL,15,F2018.
OL,17,FOn the death of 45-year-old Denise
OL,18,FGossett, Allen previously admitted
OL,19,Fmanslaughter by reason of suicide pact.
