OL,7,F"My beautiful mother was taken from
OL,8,Fme," Ms Gosset's statement read. "My
OL,9,Fyounger brother and sister, Roman and
OL,10,FSabrina, along with Sabrina's wee baby
OL,11,FMorgana are all gone too.
OL,13,F"Their four lives were taken in a fire
OL,14,Fstarted deliberately.
OL,16,F"And it breaks my heart to think on
OL,17,Fwhat happened; to think on how they
OL,18,Fdied. I miss them so much. And, to be
OL,19,Fhonest, it's very difficult to convey
OL,20,Fsuch a loss in words.
