OL,3,C'My heart breaks thinking of how they
OL,4,Cdied' says woman of family killed in
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,F"My remaining family and I are
OL,8,Fincredibly thankful for everything the
OL,9,Fpolice, and those who helped bring
OL,10,Fthis to court, have done.
OL,12,F"It is hard to move on with our lives,
OL,13,Fand my life will never be the same
OL,14,Fagain. But the support of everyone,
OL,15,Fespecially my partner and friends, has
OL,16,Ftruly meant such a lot."
OL,18,FAllen, whose address was given as HMP
OL,19,FMaghaberry, also admitted arson with
OL,20,Fintent to endanger life.
