OL,7,FHe appeared in the dock at Belfast
OL,8,FCrown Court on Wednesday for
OL,9,Fsentencing.
OL,11,FMr Justice O'Hara said Allen came from
OL,12,Fan "unstable, unhappy background", and
OL,13,F"lived most of his life online ... in
OL,14,Fa fantasy world" because of isolation
OL,15,Ffrom others.
OL,17,FBut the judge said the killings
OL,18,Frequired planning, and could not be
OL,19,Fexplained by a "sudden detachment from
OL,20,Freality or loss of control".
