OL,7,F"There is a very dangerous and
OL,8,Fdisturbing part of his make-up that
OL,9,Fled to these murders," he added.
OL,11,FMr Justice O'Hara said Allen would
OL,12,Fserve 29 years in prison before he
OL,13,Fcould be considered for release.
OL,15,FTaking into account time already
OL,16,Fserved, the judge said Allen would not
OL,17,Fbe eligible for parole until 2047.
OL,19,FDetective Inspector Hazel Miller said
OL,20,FAllen had been held accountable for
OL,21,Fhis actions.
