OL,4,Cdied' says woman of family killed in
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,F"Three generations ` a mother, her two
OL,8,Fchildren and her granddaughter `
OL,9,Fperished in a fire deliberately
OL,10,Fstarted by Daniel Allen in their home
OL,11,Fin Derrylin," she said.
OL,13,F"This was a horrific and cruel act.
OL,14,FIt's hard to even begin to imagine the
OL,15,Fpanic, fear and sheer suffering.
OL,17,F"With the use of forensic evidence,
OL,18,Fand working in partnership with the
OL,19,FPublic Prosecution Service, Daniel
OL,20,FAllen has today been held accountable
OL,21,Ffor his actions.
