OL,7,F"I'm deeply mindful, however, that
OL,8,Fthis is an event that will never be
OL,9,Fforgotten. We've seen destruction and
OL,10,Fa loss beyond words.
OL,12,F"My thoughts are with the remaining
OL,13,Ffamily members, whose lives won't ever
OL,14,Fbe the same."
